OL,3,CFood Costs: Can You Spend Less?
OL,5,FThe average weekly food cost for the
OL,6,Ftypical UK household is #103, an
OL,7,Fincrease of 18% from a year ago. We'll
OL,8,Fmeet the Thomas family in Oxford who
OL,9,Fhave noticed that their weekly food
OL,10,Fshop for four has crept up to around
OL,11,F#200 a month.
OL,13,FThey'll be paid a visit from Mitch
OL,14,FLane, known as @mealsbymitch on
OL,15,FTikTok, who has made a name for
OL,16,Fhimself on social media by coming up
OL,17,Fwith recipes that can feed a family of
OL,18,Ffour for just five pounds.
