OL,3,CFood Costs: Can You Spend Less?
OL,5,FAs well as shopping smarter, another
OL,6,Fway to save money is by making sure
OL,7,Fthat what you do buy doesn't go to
OL,8,Fwaste. According to sustainability
OL,9,Fcharity Wrap, the average household
OL,10,Fwastes an estimated #700 every year
OL,11,Fsimply by throwing food away.
OL,13,FWe'll meet Kate Hall, author of The
OL,14,FFull Freezer Method. In a bid to
OL,15,Freduce food waste and save money,
OL,16,FKate's mission is to spread awareness
OL,17,Fof the surprising food items that can
OL,18,Fbe frozen, and what tricks you can use
OL,19,Fto do this even in the smallest
OL,20,Ffreezers.
